{"tid":1396660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"18個環保團體響應8月5日罷工","createTime":"2019-08-02T07:21:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T09:03:07.000Z","uid":212626,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a30c7f23d9637bd483c2d4306e8e0a68c696523b","tid":1396660,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T07:21:28.000Z","msg":"反對修訂《逃犯條例》風波未見平息，網上號召下周一（5日）全港罷工、罷市及罷課，同時於本港7個地區舉行集會，要求政府回應「反修例」五大訴求。<span style=\"color: red;\">18個環保團體響應罷工行動</span>，包括「土地正義聯盟 」﹑「健康空氣行動」，「長春社」﹑「食德好」﹑「綠色力量」﹑ 「綠領行動」等。<br />\n<br />\n其中「健康空氣行動」在Facebook專頁帖文，對香港現狀深表痛心，亦香港政府無視元朗發生的暴力事件深表憤慨，作為關心城市發展的一份子，必須與所有愛護香港的人同行。<br />\n<br />\n帖文怖內容提及，1925年的省港大罷工，令當時殖民政府不得不回應華工的訴求。要保護前線同行者不落單，團體別無選擇，希望取態獲支持者認同，因此響應下周一的罷工行動。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">響應8月5日罷工的環保團體包括：<br />\n<br />\n大嶼山愛護水牛協會 Lantau Buffalo Association<br />\n生態巴士 ecobus<br />\n生態教育及資源中心 Eco-Education and Resources Centre (ERC)<br />\n守護大嶼聯盟 Save Lantau Alliance <br />\n自然脈絡 Natural Network <br />\n長春社 The Conservancy Association<br />\n食德好 Food Grace <br />\n香港自然生態論壇 <a href=\"http://HKWildlife.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FHKWildlife.net&d=7fFLqiM2ByXH61viL1oyjMg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=a5b28192\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">HKWildlife.net</a> <br />\n香港海豚保育學會 Hong Kong Dolphin Conservation Society <br />\n健康空氣行動 Clean Air Network <br />\n創建香港 Designing Hong Kong <br />\n綠色力量 Green Power<br />\n綠領行動 Greeners Action - 全新專頁 <br />\n龍尾環境教育中心 Lung Mei Environmental Education Centre<br />\n環保觸覺 Green Sense<br />\n土地正義聯盟 Land Justice League<br />\n香港自然探索學會 Society of Hong Kong Nature Explorers</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qyZwpgr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqyZwpgr.jpg&h=3ed49a82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2417738/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2417738%2F&d=7fFLqiM2ByXH61viL1oyjMg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=7aac29f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2417738/</a>"},{"pid":"e2e29d7b773b2c7d524e068f14882bdeecfd595a","tid":1396660,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T07:23:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0088fb4e41bdc35d6eac71a84bd112c6159ec2c2","tid":1396660,"uid":210254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T07:28:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28af5cf3bbe063485e1b387252fe70b49b2fa45e","tid":1396660,"uid":258362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:03:07.000Z","msg":"有公務員文宣<br />\n一人一Email請公務員罷工<br />\n<br />\n得。番。一。個。鐘！！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「救人！」世紀最大救義士唯一方法 正式上線 第三波<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1395699\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1395699</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}